    <div class="active" id="shownews">
      <h1 class="title">潍坊市博物馆荣获2016年度全省单位内部治安保卫工作成绩突出集体称号</h1>
      <div class="editor"><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">&nbsp; &nbsp; 日前，</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">山东</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">省公安厅印发《关于</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">表扬</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">全省单位内部治安保卫工作</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">成绩突出</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">集体和个人的</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">通报</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">》（</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">鲁</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">公通〔</span>201</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">7</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">〕</span>27<span style="font-family:仿宋">号），我</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">馆保卫科再获殊荣，</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">荣获</span>201</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">6</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">年度全省单位内部治安保卫工作</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">成绩突出</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">集体称号，受到</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">山东</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">省公安厅通报表彰。这是我</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">馆保卫科自</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">2015<span style="font-family:仿宋">年</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">12</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">月荣获</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">山东省工人先锋号荣誉</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">称号之后，在安全保卫工作方面获得的又一项</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">重要</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">省级殊荣</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">，潍坊市所有企事业单位仅三家，全省博物馆系统唯此一家。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:仿宋">近年来，</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">我</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">馆</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">高度重视</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">安全</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">保卫工作</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">，</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">把文物安全工作放在各项工作的首位，</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">强调</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">安全是立馆之本、是重中之重，是文物工作的生命线，</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">认真贯彻落实国务院《企事业单位内部治安保卫条例》，坚持</span>“一岗双责”原则，明确责任主体，把安全责任落实到每一岗位</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">、</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">每一个人，强化隐患排查治理，及时消除安全隐患，</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">每月开展一次</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">消防安全大检查</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">；</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">全面提升改造消防设施，将原有的水淋灭火系统改为气体灭火系统，对部分防火卷帘门进行了改造升级，增设了</span>“通道<span style="font-family:Calibri">X</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">光机、安检门”等安全设备，监控系统全部更换为数字化摄像头，实现了全天候</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">360</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">°无死角覆盖；在增加安全保卫人员的基础上，提高安保人员的安保技能，定期组织安全培训、实地演练，增强防范意识及突发情况应变能力；同时增设警犬防卫，形成“人防、物防、技防、畜防”四位一体的安防体系，</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">实现了</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">多年安全无事故发生</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">，为建设平安</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">潍坊</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">作出了积极贡献。</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p><script src="/inc/AspCms_VisitsAdd.asp?id=503"></script></div>
      
      <div class="met_page">上一条：<a href="/content/?501.html">我馆活动入选全市2017年“元旦春节文化惠民活动”十大品牌</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;下一条：<a href="/content/?504.html">潍坊市博物馆三名同志被聘为首批“山东省文物修复师”</a></div>
    </div>
